text: "... and we would have got away with it, if it wasn't for you damn kids."
Approximately all western marxists swapped their cute class identity models for spicier idpol variants many decades ago. Please try to keep up.

Even were it true that a genuine chud cohort occupy "policymaking positions" in the admin, aggressively exhorting them to trade-in being chuds for something cooler doesn't seem like the truly practical way forward.

... Furthermore, if there was actually a way to deliver harsh retribution against the Woke legacy of cuck capitalism, with due discrimination, that would be great. Of course, winding back post-Renaissance financial technology to the middle ages isn't it.
Why has the left been so unable to coopt and subvert old flags, when they've been so relentlessly successful at capturing and disfiguring everything else.
The old flag of England has them flinching and sobbing like a vampire trapped in a garlic bottling plant.
Back in Ccru days there'd have been no question about it.
... I'd still be a hopeless gyno-horrorism simp if only it was vastly fangier.
CLXVIIII suffices to explain on its own why CLXIX is just wrong.
